com.devbliss.doctest.machine

Class DocTestMachineImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.devbliss.doctest.machine.DocTestMachineImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocTestMachine

    public class DocTestMachineImpl
extends Object
implements DocTestMachine
    Default implementation of DocTestMachine.

    This class ownes a list of DocItem : listItem. Each time a say method is called, a DocItem is added to listItem.
    At the end of the workflow, the method endDocTest() is called and uses a ReportRenderer to render the listItem .
